---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Plenum AI Systems — AI Growth Systems for Home Service Businesses"
  description="Plenum AI Systems, a Lead Continuity LLC company, builds AI systems that follow up faster, reactivate dead leads, and turn more interest into booked appointments for home service businesses."
  canonical="https://plenumaisystems.com">

<Nav />

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div>
      <div class="label">AI Growth Systems for Home Service Businesses</div>
      <h1>
        Leads are nice.<br>
        <span class="booked-highlight">Booked</span> is <span class="better-highlight">better.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Plenum AI Systems builds AI infrastructure for home service businesses ready to turn interest into real results. We capture every lead, follow up in under 60 seconds, and turn dead databases into revenue.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">→ Book a Free Audit</a>
        <a href="#how" class="btn btn-ghost">See How It Works</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stats">
        <div>
          <div class="hero-stat-val"><span class="blue">&lt;60s</span></div>
          <div class="hero-stat-lbl">Speed-to-lead</div>
          <div style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.65rem;color:var(--text3);margin-top:4px;">Source: <a href="https://www.leadresponsemanagement.org/lrm_study/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--blue-soft);">MIT/HBR Lead Response Study</a></div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="hero-stat-val"><span class="blue">24/7</span></div>
          <div class="hero-stat-lbl">AI coverage</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="hero-stat-val"><span class="blue">0</span></div>
          <div class="hero-stat-lbl">Software to install</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-visual">
      <div class="hero-mockup">
        <div class="hero-mockup-screen">
          <div style="padding:16px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;height:100%;background:var(--surface);">
            <div style="text-align:center;font-size:0.7rem;color:var(--text3);margin-top:8px;">SMS Conversation</div>
            <div style="display:flex;justify-content:flex-end;">
              <div style="max-width:80%;font-size:0.75rem;line-height:1.4;padding:10px 13px;border-radius:14px 14px 4px 14px;background:var(--blue);color:#fff;">
                Hi Sarah, it's from XYZ HVAC. We still have your maintenance consult on file. Want us to hold a spot this week?
              </div>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;justify-content:flex-start;">
              <div style="max-width:80%;font-size:0.75rem;line-height:1.4;padding:10px 13px;border-radius:14px 14px 14px 4px;background:var(--surface-2);color:var(--text);border:1px solid var(--border);">
                Yes, do you have Thursday?
              </div>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;justify-content:flex-end;">
              <div style="max-width:80%;font-size:0.75rem;line-height:1.4;padding:10px 13px;border-radius:14px 14px 4px 14px;background:var(--blue);color:#fff;">
                Thursday at 2:00pm is open. You're booked in.
              </div>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-top:auto;padding:10px 12px;background:var(--orange);border:1px solid var(--orange);border-radius:var(--radius);text-align:center;">
              <div style="font-size:0.65rem;font-weight:600;color:#fff;letter-spacing:0.5px;text-transform:uppercase;">Book Now</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="floating-chip floating-chip-1">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;">
          <div style="width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:var(--radius);background:var(--blue-bg);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:var(--blue);">📅</div>
          <div style="line-height:1.25;">
            <div style="font-size:0.8rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);">New Booking</div>
            <div style="font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--text3);">HVAC Tune-up · Tue 2:00pm</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="floating-chip floating-chip-2">
        <div style="font-size:0.65rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.6px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text3);margin-bottom:4px;">Campaign</div>
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:8px;">
          <span style="font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:500;color:var(--text);">+87%</span>
          <span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:3px;font-size:0.8rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--green);;">↑ leads booked</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="alt" id="problem">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div>
        <div class="label">The Real Problem</div>
        <h2>It's not a lead problem.</h2>
        <p>Most home service businesses generate plenty of interest. Then it leaks. Old leads sit untouched, inquiries wait too long, missed calls never get recovered, and reviews get requested whenever someone remembers. That is not a marketing strategy. It is an expensive way to lose revenue you already paid to create.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:16px;">Plenum AI Systems follows up faster, reactivates warm prospects, and turns more interest into booked appointments.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="position:relative;border-radius:var(--radius-xl);padding:36px;background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;padding:13px 18px;background:var(--surface-2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-lg); margin-bottom:22px;">
          <span style="color:var(--text);">📊</span>
          <span style="font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);">A typical funnel · last 30 days</span>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:18px;">
          <div>
            <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:8px;">
              <span style="font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--text2);">Leads captured</span>
              <span style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:1.2rem;color:var(--text);">248</span>
            </div>
            <div style="height:8px;border-radius:var(--radius-full);background:var(--surface-2);overflow:hidden;">
              <div style="width:100%;height:100%;border-radius:var(--radius-full);background:var(--blue);"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:8px;">
              <span style="font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--text2);">Replied to in time</span>
              <div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:6px;">
                <span style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:1.2rem;color:var(--text);">71</span>
                <span style="font-size:0.72rem;color:var(--text3);">(29%)</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div style="height:8px;border-radius:var(--radius-full);background:var(--surface-2);overflow:hidden;">
              <div style="width:29%;height:100%;border-radius:var(--radius-full);background:var(--border-2);"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:8px;">
              <span style="font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--text2);">Actually booked</span>
              <div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:6px;">
                <span style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:1.2rem;color:var(--orange);">23</span>
                <span style="font-size:0.72rem;color:var(--text3);">(9%)</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div style="height:8px;border-radius:var(--radius-full);background:var(--surface-2);overflow:hidden;">
              <div style="width:9%;height:100%;border-radius:var(--radius-full);background:var(--orange);"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;margin:22px 0 0;padding:12px 14px;background:var(--surface-2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);">
          <span style="color:var(--orange);font-size:1.2rem;">⚠</span>
          <span style="font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--text2);"><strong style="font-weight:600;color:var(--text);">177 leads</strong> went cold waiting for a reply.</span>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top:16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.65rem;color:var(--text3);">Sources: <a href="https://www.leadresponsemanagement.org/lrm_study/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--blue-soft);">LRM Study</a> · <a href="https://hbr.org/2011/03/the-short-life-of-online-sales-leads" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--blue-soft);">HBR</a></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="services">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="max-width:660px;margin-bottom:56px;">
      <div class="label">The System</div>
      <h2>Five services. One growth system.</h2>
      <p>We don't sell a random tactic and call it a strategy. We connect the pieces that actually fill your calendar.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="accordion-sticky-wrap">
      <div class="accordion">
        <div class="accordion-item active" onclick="toggleAccordion(this)">
          <div class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-number">01</span>
            <div class="accordion-title">
              <h3>Outreach Specialist</h3>
              <div class="accordion-subtitle">Database Reactivation</div>
            </div>
            <span class="accordion-arrow">→</span>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-body">
            <div class="accordion-body-inner">
              <p>We re-engage old leads, no-shows, and past customers with AI-powered SMS follow-up. Your database is buried revenue, not a junk list.</p>
              <p class="sub-quote">"3 spots left this month — interested?" The AI handles objections in real time and routes hot leads to your calendar.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item" onclick="toggleAccordion(this)">
          <div class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-number">02</span>
            <div class="accordion-title">
              <h3>Reputation Manager</h3>
              <div class="accordion-subtitle">Reviews & Referrals</div>
            </div>
            <span class="accordion-arrow">→</span>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-body">
            <div class="accordion-body-inner">
              <p>We generate more Google reviews and referrals automatically, so trust isn't left to chance. Job marked complete → review request fires automatically.</p>
              <p class="sub-quote">Being great is one thing. Looking great when people Google you is what books the appointment.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item" onclick="toggleAccordion(this)">
          <div class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-number">03</span>
            <div class="accordion-title">
              <h3>Website Manager</h3>
              <div class="accordion-subtitle">Lead Nurturing</div>
            </div>
            <span class="accordion-arrow">→</span>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-body">
            <div class="accordion-body-inner">
              <p>We follow up with new web leads instantly, answer common questions, and guide them to booking while interest is still hot.</p>
              <p class="sub-quote">Responding fast. Crazy concept, apparently.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item" onclick="toggleAccordion(this)">
          <div class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-number">04</span>
            <div class="accordion-title">
              <h3>AI Receptionist</h3>
              <div class="accordion-subtitle">Missed Call Text-Back</div>
            </div>
            <span class="accordion-arrow">→</span>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-body">
            <div class="accordion-body-inner">
              <p>When your team can't pick up, we text the caller back instantly and start the conversation. Under 60 seconds.</p>
              <p class="sub-quote">Silence isn't a follow-up strategy. It's a referral program for your competitors.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item" onclick="toggleAccordion(this)">
          <div class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-number">05</span>
            <div class="accordion-title">
              <h3>Marketing Director</h3>
              <div class="accordion-subtitle">Paid Ads & AI Nurturing</div>
            </div>
            <span class="accordion-arrow">→</span>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-body">
            <div class="accordion-body-inner">
              <p>We test ad angles, double down on what books consults, and wire campaigns to AI follow-up. A lead without follow-up isn't a lead.</p>
              <p class="sub-quote">Every ad dollar should fill your calendar. We make sure it does.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="accordion-sticky-panel">
        <div class="sticky-inner">
          <div class="artifact active" data-artifact="1" style="width:100%;max-width:432px;background:var(--surface);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);border:1px solid var(--border);overflow:hidden;">
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:13px 18px;background:var(--surface-2);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);">
              <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;">
                <span style="color:var(--blue);">⚡</span>
                <span style="font-size:0.8rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);">Reactivation Feed</span>
              </div>
              <div style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;background:var(--green-bg);border:1px solid rgba(92,224,168,0.2);border-radius:var(--radius-full);padding:4px 10px;">
                <span style="width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--green);"></span>
                <span style="font-size:0.65rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--green);">LIVE</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div style="padding:14px 18px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;">
              <div style="display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:flex-start;">
                <div style="width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--blue);margin-top:6px;flex-shrink:0;"></div>
                <div style="flex:1;">
                  <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:baseline;">
                    <span style="font-size:0.78rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);">Mike T. — Tulsa</span>
                    <span style="font-size:0.65rem;color:var(--text3);">2m ago</span>
                  </div>
                  <div style="font-size:0.72rem;color:var(--text2);margin-top:2px;">AI sent reactivation SMS → <span style="color:var(--green);">replied "Yes"</span></div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div style="display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:flex-start;">
                <div style="width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--blue);margin-top:6px;flex-shrink:0;"></div>
                <div style="flex:1;">
                  <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:baseline;">
                    <span style="font-size:0.78rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);">David R. — Broken Arrow</span>
                    <span style="font-size:0.65rem;color:var(--text3);">7m ago</span>
                  </div>
                  <div style="font-size:0.72rem;color:var(--text2);margin-top:2px;">AI called → booked estimate for <span style="color:var(--orange);">Thu 10am</span></div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div style="display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:flex-start;">
                <div style="width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--orange);margin-top:6px;flex-shrink:0;"></div>
                <div style="flex:1;">
                  <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:baseline;">
                    <span style="font-size:0.78rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);">Jennifer K. — Owasso</span>
                    <span style="font-size:0.65rem;color:var(--text3);">12m ago</span>
                  </div>
                  <div style="font-size:0.72rem;color:var(--text2);margin-top:2px;">AI sent 2nd follow-up → <span style="color:var(--text3);">opened, no reply</span></div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div style="display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:flex-start;">
                <div style="width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--blue);margin-top:6px;flex-shrink:0;"></div>
                <div style="flex:1;">
                  <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:baseline;">
                    <span style="font-size:0.78rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);">Carlos M. — Bixby</span>
                    <span style="font-size:0.65rem;color:var(--text3);">18m ago</span>
                  </div>
                  <div style="font-size:0.72rem;color:var(--text2);margin-top:2px;">AI reactivated 6mo cold lead → <span style="color:var(--green);">booked next week</span></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div style="border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding:10px 18px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;">
              <div style="font-size:0.7rem;color:var(--text3);"><span style="font-weight:600;color:var(--green);">+14</span> leads contacted today</div>
              <div style="font-size:0.7rem;color:var(--blue);">Database: 1,847 leads</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="artifact" data-artifact="2" style="display:none;width:100%;max-width:432px;background:var(--surface);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);border:1px solid var(--border);overflow:hidden;">
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;padding:13px 18px;background:var(--surface-2);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);">
              <span style="color:var(--text);">⭐</span>
              <span style="font-size:0.8rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);">Reputation · Google</span>
            </div>
            <div style="padding:18px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;">
              <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;">
                <span style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:1.8rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1;">4.9</span>
                <div>
                  <div style="color:var(--orange);font-size:0.85rem;">★★★★★</div>
                  <div style="font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--text3);margin-top:3px;">Based on 218 reviews</div>
                </div>
                <div style="margin-left:auto;">
                  <div style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;background:var(--surface-2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-full);padding:5px 12px;">
                    <span style="font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--green);;">↑</span>
                    <span style="font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);">+34 this month</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div style="display:flex;gap:11px;padding:12px 14px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);">
                <div style="width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--blue-bg);flex-shrink:0;"></div>
                <div>
                  <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;">
                    <span style="font-size:0.8rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);">Mike R.</span>
                    <span style="color:var(--orange);font-size:0.6rem;">★★★★★</span>
                  </div>
                  <div style="font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--text2);margin-top:3px;line-height:1.4;">Booking was easy and the team was lovely. Already rebooked.</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="artifact" data-artifact="3" style="display:none;width:100%;max-width:432px;background:var(--surface);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);border:1px solid var(--border);overflow:hidden;">
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;padding:13px 18px;background:var(--surface-2);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);">
              <span style="color:var(--text);">🌐</span>
              <span style="font-size:0.8rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);">New lead · instant response</span>
            </div>
            <div style="padding:18px;">
              <div style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:500;color:var(--text);line-height:1.15;">Book Your Service</div>
              <div style="font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--text3);margin-top:6px;">We'll text you back in under a minute.</div>
              <div style="margin-top:14px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:9px;">
                <div style="height:38px;border-radius:var(--radius);display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 12px;font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--text3);border:1px solid var(--border);">Full name</div>
                <div style="height:38px;border-radius:var(--radius);display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 12px;font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--text3);border:1px solid var(--border);">Mobile number</div>
                <div style="background:var(--orange);color:#fff;text-align:center;font-size:0.85rem;font-weight:600;padding:11px;border-radius:var(--radius);">Request my appointment</div>
              </div>
              <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;margin-top:14px;padding:10px 12px;background:var(--surface-2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);">
                <span style="color:var(--orange);font-size:0.8rem;">💬</span>
                <span style="font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--text2);">"Thanks! What's the best time for you?"</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="artifact" data-artifact="4" style="display:none;width:100%;max-width:432px;background:var(--surface);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);border:1px solid var(--border);overflow:hidden;">
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;padding:13px 18px;background:var(--surface-2);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);">
              <span style="color:var(--text);">📞</span>
              <span style="font-size:0.8rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);">Missed call · auto text-back</span>
            </div>
            <div style="padding:18px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;">
              <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;padding:12px 14px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);">
                <div style="width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--orange-bg);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;color:var(--orange);">📵</div>
                <div style="line-height:1.3;">
                  <div style="font-size:0.85rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);">Missed call</div>
                  <div style="font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--text3);">(307) 555-0148 · 14s ago</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div style="display:flex;justify-content:flex-end;">
                <div style="max-width:82%;font-size:0.8rem;line-height:1.45;padding:10px 13px;border-radius:14px 14px 4px 14px;background:var(--orange);color:#fff;">Sorry we missed you. This is XYZ HVAC. Can we help you book a service call?</div>
              </div>
              <div style="display:flex;justify-content:flex-start;">
                <div style="max-width:82%;font-size:0.8rem;line-height:1.45;padding:10px 13px;border-radius:14px 14px 14px 4px;background:var(--surface-2);color:var(--text);border:1px solid var(--border);">Yes, I need a tune-up.</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;background:var(--surface-2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-full);padding:5px 12px;">
